{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"story_beewax_set_1_story_1","storyGroup":"story_beewax_set_1","storySort":0,"storyDependence":null,"storyCanShow":0,"storyCode":null,"storyName":"黄沙归途","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"为了送一位感染者的遗物回到家乡，蜜蜡步上了一段未知的旅途。","storyCanEnter":0,"storyTxt":"obt/memory/story_beewax_1_1","avgTag":"幕间","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":0,"requiredStages":null,"characters":["安克赫娜","办事处干员","见多识广的老人","驮兽","博闻强识的妇人","沙漠行商","？？？","部族祭司","忧愁的老人","部落长老","卡涅利安"]},"lines":[{"type":"HEADER","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"Dialog","id":3},{"type":"Background","image":"31_g2_luo_reception","screenadapt":"coverall","id":4},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":5},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$path_intro","key":"$path_loop","volume":"0.4","id":6,"musicid":0},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":7},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":8},{"type":"Text","text":"罗德岛驻萨尔贡某办事处","id":9},{"type":"Dialog","id":10},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#1$1","fadetime":"1.5","id":11},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":12},{"type":"multiline","name":"安克赫娜","text":"嗯......刷子、精油、磨砂石，都带好了。","id":13},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#2$1","id":14},{"type":"multiline","name":"安克赫娜","text":"咦？小虫子，怎么跑到包裹里来了，你要和我一起走吗？不行哦，快走开快走开。","id":15},{"type":"Dialog","id":16},{"type":"Dialog","id":17},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_clothmovement","volume":"1","id":18},{"type":"move","name":"middle","xpos":"-15","fadetime":"0.2","block":"true","id":19},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"0.2","block":"true","id":20},{"type":"move","name":"middle","xpos":"15","fadetime":"0.2","block":"true","id":21},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":22},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#7$1","id":23},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"好啦！都包好了。","id":24},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#2$1","id":25},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"不行，再等一下，临走前得好好和这里的卡蒂姆先生道别。","id":26},{"type":"Dialog","id":27},{"type":"Character","id":28},{"type":"playsound","key":"$dooropenquite","id":29},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_090","fadetime":"1.5","id":30},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":31},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"办事处干员","text":"这个混账走就走了，把东西丢到门口算什么事！","id":32},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_090","focus":"1","id":33},{"type":"jump","name":"left","power":"5","times":"2","fadetime":"0.51","block":"true","id":34},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"卡蒂姆先生，对、对不起，我不该把虫子丢到门口的！","id":35},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_090","focus":"2","id":36},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"办事处干员","text":"安克赫娜小姐，不、不是的，我不是在说你，你不要误会！","id":37},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_090","focus":"1","id":38},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"不是说我吗......卡蒂姆先生，是发生什么了？","id":39},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_090","focus":"2","id":40},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"办事处干员","text":"唉，这都是你来之前的事了，上个月在这里的一位临时干员病发去世，我打包了他的遗物准备寄回他的家乡。","id":41},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"办事处干员","text":"但本地的信使一听到物品的主人是感染者，都觉得晦气不肯寄送。明明经过处理后一点感染的风险也不会有。","id":42},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_090","focus":"1","id":43},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"可、可是你在这里做了这么多事情，派发药物，收治病人，还经常传授给大家预防的办法......","id":44},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_090","focus":"2","id":45},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"办事处干员","text":"相比矿石病在人们心中铸成的伤害与恐惧，我们所做的......实在是微不足道。","id":46},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_090","focus":"1","id":47},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"原来是这样吗......","id":48},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_090","focus":"2","id":49},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"办事处干员","text":"唉，要怪就怪我这条伤腿太不争气，不能自己去送，再等些时日吧......","id":50},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"办事处干员","text":"好了，不说这些了，看你已经打包好行李了，是打算今天就离开吗？","id":51},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_090","focus":"1","id":52},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"嗯，前天接到了从罗德岛发来的消息，姐姐不在那里，也不希望我去找她。","id":53},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"虽然并未讲清缘由，但姐姐这么做一定有自己的道理，我尊重她的选择。","id":54},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_090","focus":"2","id":55},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"办事处干员","text":"可你看起来真的很失落啊。","id":56},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_090","focus":"1","id":57},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"没、没关系的，我也有自己的试炼要完成，总是追着姐姐的脚步也实在是不像话。","id":58},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_090","focus":"2","id":59},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"办事处干员","text":"安克赫娜小姐能够这么想，就已经是很不错的一步了，往后的行程你有没有什么目标和计划？","id":60},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_090","focus":"1","id":61},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"嗯......要去哪里完全没有想过呢......没关系，路上慢慢想也来得及。","id":62},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_090","focus":"2","id":63},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"办事处干员","text":"哈哈哈，来，行李给我，让我送送你吧，这些天幸亏有你帮我，我一个人带着这条伤腿难免手忙脚乱。","id":64},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_090","focus":"1","id":65},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"没有没有，都是举手之劳，反而是我才应该好好感激卡蒂姆先生的照顾呢！说到感激......","id":66},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_090","focus":"2","id":67},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"办事处干员","text":"嗨，不用，言重了......","id":68},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_090","focus":"1","id":69},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":70},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"卡蒂姆先生！","id":71},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_090","focus":"2","id":72},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"办事处干员","text":"欸？！","id":73},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_090","focus":"1","id":74},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"如果是这些遗物的话，我可以帮你送去的。","id":75},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"萨尔贡的沙漠虽然广袤无际，但是我们部族久处大漠，如何在沙漠中行进是我们从小就要学习的技能。","id":76},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_090","focus":"2","id":77},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"办事处干员","text":"这不会耽误你的试炼吗？","id":78},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#3$1","name2":"avg_npc_090","focus":"1","id":79},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"不会的，帮助别人也是试炼的一环，很重要的一环！","id":80},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#3$1","name2":"avg_npc_090","focus":"2","id":81},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"办事处干员","text":"这些话要是别人说给我听，我一定会嗤之以鼻。","id":82},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"办事处干员","text":"可是安克赫娜小姐啊......能够孤身一人从大漠深处的部落找到这里来，我实在是没有拒绝的理由。","id":83},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_090","focus":"1","id":84},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"所以呢所以呢？！","id":85},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_090","focus":"2","id":86},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"办事处干员","text":"所以我啊，只好把那家伙的东西交给你了，安克赫娜小姐，请你务必要送它们回到他的家乡啊。","id":87},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"办事处干员","text":"毕竟，这是他唯一留下的愿望了。","id":88},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_090","focus":"1","id":89},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"嗯......我知道的。","id":90},{"type":"Dialog","id":91},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":92},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":93},{"type":"Character","id":94},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_desert_3","screenadapt":"showall","id":95},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":96},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":97},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","text":"","id":98},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#1$1","id":99},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"听卡蒂姆先生的描述，要去的地方似乎是个封闭的部落，不是很确定具体的位置。","id":100},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#4$1","id":101},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"唔......虽然他叮嘱我出了村子严格按照方向牌的指示去走肯定能找到。","id":102},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"真的吗？感觉有些忐忑啊......方向牌指西是一片梭梭林，指东就是要去的红沙地。","id":103},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#1$1","id":104},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"呼......","id":105},{"type":"dialog","id":106},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_clothmovement","volume":"1","id":107},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"0.4","block":"true","id":108},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"（双手合拢）金沙之地，落日归处。神灵之眷，随行千里。","id":109},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"无颜的神灵啊，请庇佑我顺利穿过那片沙原，让漂泊多年的灵魂回到他的家乡......","id":110},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#7$1","id":111},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"出发吧。","id":112},{"type":"Dialog","id":113},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":114},{"type":"character","fadetime":"1.5","id":115},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":116},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":117},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_snowstormlp","loop":"true","channel":"a","id":118},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":119},{"type":"StopSound","channel":"a","fadetime":"1","id":120},{"type":"Text","text":"一阵风吹过，那块指示牌发出令人牙酸的吱呀声，在风中缓缓地转起了圈。","id":121},{"type":"Dialog","id":122},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":123},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":124},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":125},{"type":"Character","id":126},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_desert_1","screenadapt":"showall","id":127},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":128},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$path_intro","key":"$path_loop","volume":"0.4","id":129,"musicid":1},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":130},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","text":"","id":131},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":132},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#4$1","fadetime":"1.5","id":133},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":134},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#4$1","id":135},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"太阳......太阳又升起来了，我已经走了一天吗？放眼望去，四周都是梭梭，怎么还没走到那片红色的沙地啊？","id":136},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"卡蒂姆先生说的下一个指示牌又在哪里啊？不是说走个半天就可以见到吗？","id":137},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"好累......走不动了，得找片阴凉处坐着歇一歇。","id":138},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#1$1","id":139},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"没有具体的位置，路线又偏移了，我要怎么才能找到他的家乡啊？","id":140},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#4$1","id":141},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"要是姐姐在就好了......她在的话一定会拍拍我的脑袋告诉我没关系。","id":142},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#1$1","id":143},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"（低头看向自己的手）","id":144},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#5$1","id":145},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"嗯......也不是不可以。","id":146},{"type":"dialog","id":147},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#1$1","id":148},{"type":"jump","name":"middle","power":"2","times":"3","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":149},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"（手放在自己脑袋上拍拍）","id":150},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#5$1","id":151},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"没关系，安克赫娜，不要沮丧。","id":152},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"冷静下来，会有办法的，站起来看看四周的环境，从中寻找头绪。","id":153},{"type":"multiline","name":"安克赫娜","text":"好，先站起来——","id":154},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#2$1","id":155},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":156},{"type":"move","name":"middle","ypos":"-10","fadetime":"0.3","isblock":"false","id":157},{"type":"multiline","name":"安克赫娜","text":"呜哇！","id":158},{"type":"Dialog","id":159},{"type":"Dialog","id":160},{"type":"move","name":"middle","ypos":"10","fadetime":"1","isblock":"true","id":161},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#4$1","id":162},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"痛、好痛，踩到衣摆了。","id":163},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#1$1","id":164},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"糟糕，东西都撒出来了，得赶快捡起来才行。","id":165},{"type":"Dialog","id":166},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_snowstormlp","loop":"true","channel":"a","id":167},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":168},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.5","id":169},{"type":"StopSound","channel":"a","fadetime":"0.5","id":170},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#2$1","id":171},{"type":"jump","name":"middle","power":"5","times":"2","fadetime":"0.51","block":"true","id":172},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"哇，不要跑啊，怎么这个时候刮起了风。","id":173},{"type":"Dialog","id":174},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_clothmovement","volume":"1","id":175},{"type":"move","name":"middle","xpos":"-15","fadetime":"0.2","block":"true","id":176},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"0.2","block":"true","id":177},{"type":"move","name":"middle","xpos":"15","fadetime":"0.2","block":"true","id":178},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":179},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#4$1","id":180},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"这是......日记吗？对不起，先生，我不是故意要看的，是风把纸页吹起来的。","id":181},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#4$1","id":182},{"type":"playsound","key":"$book_close","id":183},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"（合上笔记本）","id":184},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#6$1","id":185},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"......刚刚那一小段，是那位先生对自己家乡的记述吗？说不定......我可以从里面找到一些线索。","id":186},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#1$1","id":187},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"神灵啊，请您原谅我对亡者的冒犯。","id":188},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#1$1","id":189},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_paper1","volume":"1","id":190},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"（打开笔记本）","id":191},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"“无数次梦中，我回到家，母亲就站在那片椰枣林下等我归来，正如当初目送我离开。”","id":192},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"“我的身体一日不如一日，对那片绿洲的思念却越发强烈，我为了梦想离开她，却在离开后的每一个夜晚梦到她。”","id":193},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"“雨季和旱季交替，积水蓄成湖泊，而后又迅速干涸为盐滩......”","id":194},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"他真的很怀念那里啊，几乎整本日记都是在家乡的往事。","id":195},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#6$1","id":196},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"椰枣林、绿洲、时令湖......","id":197},{"type":"Dialog","id":198},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":199},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":200},{"type":"Character","id":201},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_laccolith","screenadapt":"showall","id":202},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":203},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":204},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","text":"","id":205},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#1$1","id":206},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"这里有小虫子爬行......","id":207},{"type":"Dialog","id":208},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#1$1","id":209},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_clothmovement","volume":"1","id":210},{"type":"move","name":"middle","ypos":"-15","fadetime":"0.2","block":"true","id":211},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"0.2","block":"true","id":212},{"type":"move","name":"middle","ypos":"15","fadetime":"0.2","block":"true","id":213},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":214},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"（抓起来仔细端详）","id":215},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#7$1","id":216},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"应该离水源不远了，运气好的话，或许能碰到聚落。","id":217},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"要翻越好几座沙丘啊，还好带了滑沙的木板。","id":218},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"敲敲，嗯......还得好好再绑一绑。","id":219},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#1$1","id":220},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"接下来可能会有点颠簸，得把衣服挽起来，再摔倒就不好了。","id":221},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#5$1","id":222},{"type":"multiline","name":"安克赫娜","text":"好......","id":223},{"type":"multiline","name":"安克赫娜","delay":"0.3","text":"一、二、三，","id":224},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#2$1","id":225},{"type":"move","name":"middle","xpos":"1000","fadetime":"0.8","id":226},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.8","xstrength":"50","ystrength":"50","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":227},{"type":"multiline","name":"安克赫娜","delay":"0.1","text":"呜哇哇哇哇——！","id":228},{"type":"Dialog","id":229},{"type":"Dialog","id":230},{"type":"Dialog","id":231},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":232},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":233},{"type":"Character","id":234},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_desert_1","screenadapt":"showall","id":235},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.51","id":236},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":237},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","text":"","id":238},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"见多识广的老人","text":"这里提到的小镇啊......让我想想，我是去过的，过了这么多年也不知道还在不在。","id":239},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#1$1","id":240},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"老人家，您知道怎么去吗？","id":241},{"type":"Character","id":242},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"见多识广的老人","text":"骑着驮兽一路往西北方向去，遇到一座形似蘑菇的岩体后，再往西南走个几公里应该就能到了。","id":243},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#4$1","id":244},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"那您对这个小镇附近的环境有印象吗？有没有一片椰枣林？雨季的时候周边会出现时令湖吗？","id":245},{"type":"Character","id":246},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"见多识广的老人","text":"没有印象，不好意思。","id":247},{"type":"Dialog","id":248},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":249},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":250},{"type":"Character","id":251},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_desert_3","screenadapt":"showall","id":252},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.51","id":253},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":254},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","text":"","id":255},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#1$1","id":256},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_paper1","volume":"1","id":257},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"“绝望之际，卡蒂姆先生救了我。”","id":258},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"“在办事处一段时间后，我的病情趋于稳定，心情也逐渐平静......”","id":259},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#4$1","id":260},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"看起来，他之后就一直生活在办事处，直到离世。","id":261},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#4$1","focus":"-1","id":262},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"驮兽","text":"噗噗——","id":263},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#7$1","id":264},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"咦，你饿了吗？我这里还有些干草。","id":265},{"type":"Dialog","id":266},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_clothmovement","volume":"1","id":267},{"type":"move","name":"middle","xpos":"-15","fadetime":"0.2","block":"true","id":268},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"0.2","block":"true","id":269},{"type":"move","name":"middle","xpos":"15","fadetime":"0.2","block":"true","id":270},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":271},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#7$1","focus":"-1","id":272},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"驮兽","text":"（咀嚼）","id":273},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#3$1","id":274},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"你看你吃的，一地唾沫。","id":275},{"type":"Dialog","id":276},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":277},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":278},{"type":"Character","id":279},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_desert_1","screenadapt":"showall","id":280},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.51","id":281},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":282},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","text":"","id":283},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"博闻强识的妇人","text":"你要找的地方不好找啊，小姑娘。镇子的北面分布着大大小小好几个绿洲，几乎每一处都有大片的椰枣林。","id":284},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#1$1","id":285},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"那......如果加上时令湖这个条件，是不是能筛掉一些地方？","id":286},{"type":"character","id":287},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"博闻强识的妇人","text":"很难，时令湖的位置从不固定，拿它当坐标并不靠谱。","id":288},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#1$1","id":289},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"如果不介意的话，可以麻烦您在这张地图上圈出这些绿洲的大概位置吗？","id":290},{"type":"character","id":291},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"博闻强识的妇人","text":"你难道要一个个去找吗？","id":292},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#7$1","id":293},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"嗯，我答应过别人，就一定要办到。","id":294},{"type":"Dialog","id":295},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":296},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":297},{"type":"Character","id":298},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_desert_1","screenadapt":"showall","id":299},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.51","id":300},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":301},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","text":"","id":302},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#1$1","id":303},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"“终于，我攒够了离开这里的钱，我不知道这片沙漠对面有什么，但正是那些未知的事物，令我心痒难耐。”","id":304},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"“但愿我的一腔热血能有所收获，再见了，我的故乡。”","id":305},{"type":"character","id":306},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"沙漠行商","text":"嘿，小姑娘，你在念什么？","id":307},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#6$1","id":308},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"是......一位先生的过往。","id":309},{"type":"character","id":310},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"沙漠行商","text":"啊？","id":311},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#1$1","id":312},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"......就是日记。","id":313},{"type":"character","id":314},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"沙漠行商","text":"无论是什么你都得停下了，你要去的地方就在这附近，小姑娘，我们还要赶路，就把你放在这里了。","id":315},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#7$1","id":316},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"大叔，谢谢您捎我这一程。","id":317},{"type":"character","id":318},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"沙漠行商","text":"哈哈哈，哪里的话，要不是你从流沙中救起了我的车队，我早就命丧黄沙了。","id":319},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#7$1","id":320},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"愿这片沙地庇佑您接下来的旅程！！","id":321},{"type":"dialog","id":322},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_clothmovement","volume":"1","id":323},{"type":"jump","name":"middle","xpos":"-30","ypos":"-10","times":"1","fadetime":"0.7","id":324},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0.5","id":325},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":326},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"沙漠行商","text":"哈哈，谢谢！！","id":327},{"type":"Dialog","id":328},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$motorbikestart","volume":"1","id":329},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":330},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#1$1","id":331},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"这就是最后一处绿洲了，无颜的神灵，请您不吝，赐我一个奇迹吧。","id":332},{"type":"Dialog","id":333},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":334},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":335},{"type":"Character","id":336},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_village_2","screenadapt":"showall","id":337},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.51","id":338},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":339},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","text":"","id":340},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$leaveshake","volume":"0.6","id":341},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#1$1","fadetime":"1","id":342},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":343},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"您好，请问有人在吗？","id":344},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#4$1","id":345},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"有人吗？","id":346},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"看这里破败的样子，根本不像有人居住啊。","id":347},{"type":"Dialog","id":348},{"type":"character","id":349},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":350},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$leaveshake","volume":"0.6","id":351},{"type":"Delay","time":"1.5","id":352},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#5$1","id":353},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"嗯......？","id":354},{"type":"Dialog","id":355},{"type":"character","id":356},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$leaveshake","volume":"0.6","id":357},{"type":"Delay","time":"1.5","id":358},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#5$1","id":359},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"是谁？","id":360},{"type":"dialog","id":361},{"type":"Character","id":362},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":363},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"0.6","block":"false","id":364},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"true","id":365},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$fightgeneral","text":"","id":366},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":367},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"0.6","block":"false","id":368},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"true","id":369},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$fightgeneral","text":"","id":370},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"啊！","id":371},{"type":"Dialog","id":372},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$bodyfalldown1","text":"","id":373},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":374},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":375},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_clothmovement","volume":"1","id":376},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_070","fadetime":"1.5","id":377},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":378},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"是你未经允许进入了我们部族的领地，异族人。","id":379},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_070","focus":"1","id":380},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"我、我一路上过来都没有看到人，就以为是无主的绿洲。","id":381},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_070","focus":"2","id":382},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"你当然看不到。","id":383},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_070","focus":"1","id":384},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"怎么会这样？！","id":385},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_070","focus":"2","id":386},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"哼，问话前不如先收起你的长杖。","id":387},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_070","focus":"1","id":388},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"呜......好。","id":389},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_070","focus":"2","id":390},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"（明明是我受制于她，怎么这丫头反而一脸委屈？）","id":391},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"异族人，你来这里到底有何贵干？","id":392},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_070","focus":"1","id":393},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"我接到委托，要送一位先生的遗物回到他的故乡。","id":394},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"东西都在这个包里了，您看一眼吧，如果他不是这里的人，我立刻就走。","id":395},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_070","focus":"2","id":396},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"拿过来吧，让我看看。","id":397},{"type":"Dialog","id":398},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_070","id":399},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_clothmovement","volume":"1","id":400},{"type":"move","name":"left","xpos":"15","fadetime":"0.5","isblock":"true","id":401},{"type":"move","name":"left","xpos":"-15","fadetime":"0.5","isblock":"true","id":402},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":403},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_paper1","volume":"1","id":404},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":405},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$distressed_intro","key":"$distressed_loop","volume":"0.4","id":406,"musicid":2},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":407},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_070","focus":"2","id":408},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"有这么多年不曾归来，原来他已经离世了啊。","id":409},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_070","focus":"1","id":410},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"您知道他？","id":411},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_070","focus":"2","id":412},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"嗯， 按辈分，他算我的堂弟。他母亲离世前一直也是我在照顾。","id":413},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_070","focus":"1","id":414},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"除了您，他还有别的亲人吗？","id":415},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_070","focus":"2","id":416},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"（摇头）","id":417},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"异族人，这个部族已经没有几个人了，年纪小的，都跑去外面讨生活了，剩下些年纪大的，也是一年少过一年。","id":418},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_070","focus":"1","id":419},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"没有人了，部族以后要怎么办？","id":420},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_070","focus":"2","id":421},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"你还不明白吗，小丫头？我们的部族已经快要消失了，从绿洲，从萨尔贡。","id":422},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_070","focus":"1","id":423},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"那......这些东西，要怎么办呢？","id":424},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_070","focus":"2","id":425},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"我会把这些物品埋在他母亲身边的。","id":426},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_070","focus":"1","id":427},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"（不安地捏紧长杖）既然东西送到了，那我、我还是尽早离开，不再打搅为好。","id":428},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_070","focus":"2","id":429},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"小丫头，你来都来了，留下来帮帮我吧，虽然回来的只有遗物没有遗体，但魂归故里，还是要有个体面的葬礼的。","id":430},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_070","focus":"1","id":431},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"好，没问题的，我、我都可以帮忙。","id":432},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_070","focus":"2","id":433},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"那跟我来吧，该着手准备了。","id":434},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_070","focus":"1","id":435},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"先生，我、我可以问您一个问题吗？","id":436},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_070","focus":"2","id":437},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"说吧。","id":438},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_070","focus":"1","id":439},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"如果大家都离开了，为什么您还坚持留在这里？","id":440},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_070","focus":"2","id":441},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"......我是部族的祭司啊，在部族消失前，总得有一个人继续守护它。","id":442},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"何况，万一有人想要回到这里呢？就像他一样......","id":443},{"type":"Dialog","id":444},{"type":"Dialog","id":445},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":446},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":447},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_070","id":448},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_falls_2","screenadapt":"coverall","id":449},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.51","id":450},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":451},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","text":"","id":452},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_070","focus":"2","id":453},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"部族祭司","text":"你要撒第一捧土吗，小丫头？","id":454},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_070","focus":"1","id":455},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"我、我来吗？","id":456},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_070","focus":"2","id":457},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"部族祭司","text":"你是带他回来的人，理应如此。","id":458},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_070","focus":"1","id":459},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"好的。","id":460},{"type":"Dialog","id":461},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_clothmovement","volume":"1","id":462},{"type":"move","name":"left","ypos":"6","fadetime":"0.6","isblock":"true","id":463},{"type":"move","name":"left","ypos":"-6","fadetime":"0.6","isblock":"true","id":464},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":465},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"先生，我受卡蒂姆先生之托将你的遗物带回你的家乡，如今我已到达，这一路上发生的意外请你原谅。","id":466},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_070","focus":"2","id":467},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"部族祭司","text":"......","id":468},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"部族祭司","text":"那些土地上结出的苦果，终将落回土地，深埋其下，静待发芽。","id":469},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"部族祭司","text":"我亲爱的兄弟，愿你回到慈母的怀抱，愿你在黄土下得到安息，愿你去往的地方永无呻吟。","id":470},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_070","focus":"1","id":471},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"（愿金色沙原赐福于他。）","id":472},{"type":"Dialog","id":473},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_070","focus":"2","id":474},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_clothmovement","volume":"1","id":475},{"type":"move","name":"right","ypos":"6","fadetime":"0.6","isblock":"true","id":476},{"type":"move","name":"right","ypos":"-6","fadetime":"0.6","isblock":"true","id":477},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":478},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"部族祭司","text":"很感激你愿意帮我，要去吃些东西吗？这一路上辛苦你了。","id":479},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_070","focus":"1","id":480},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"没有没有，这样的路程对于我们族人来说都是小儿科。","id":481},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_070","focus":"2","id":482},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"部族祭司","text":"我从未离开过这片绿洲，你们沙漠部落的生活方式我实在难以想象，滚滚黄沙，看了只觉得害怕。","id":483},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_070","focus":"1","id":484},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"不可怕的，沙原里居住着神灵，祂会眷顾我们的。","id":485},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_070","focus":"2","id":486},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"部族祭司","text":"原本我们深信在森林中也有神灵栖身，正因祂的庇佑，部族才得以顺利生存与发展，如今看来，我们应该是被祂遗弃在这里了。","id":487},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_070","focus":"1","id":488},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"不会的，神灵不会遗弃祂的子民。","id":489},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_070","focus":"2","id":490},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"部族祭司","text":"如果是祂的子民先抛弃了自己的信仰呢？","id":491},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_070","focus":"1","id":492},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"......你是指那些离开的人吗？","id":493},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_070","focus":"2","id":494},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"部族祭司","text":"他在外面过得好吗？","id":495},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_070","focus":"1","id":496},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"不好，他得了一种无法治愈的病，身上会长石头，很痛苦，还会传染给别人，因此处处遭人白眼。","id":497},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_070","focus":"2","id":498},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"部族祭司","text":"那他走得痛苦吗？","id":499},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_070","focus":"1","id":500},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"我不知道，我到那里的时候他已经病逝了......但是有卡蒂姆先生的照顾，应该会安稳一些，至少不是孤苦无依。","id":501},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_070","focus":"2","id":502},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"部族祭司","text":"卡蒂姆先生又是谁？","id":503},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_070","focus":"1","id":504},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"是他工作地点的负责人，对矿石病的医治很有经验。","id":505},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_070","focus":"2","id":506},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"部族祭司","text":"我从前一直埋怨他不愿回来见自己母亲最后一面，明明信里提到过自己落脚的地方距离这里步行只要一天。","id":507},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_070","focus":"1","id":508},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"欸？！","id":509},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_070","focus":"1","id":510},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"居然......这么近吗？呜......实不相瞒，我走到半路迷路了，找到这里足足花了我半个多月。","id":511},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_070","focus":"2","id":512},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"部族祭司","text":"或许寄出那封信后，他又动身去往其他的地方了吧。","id":513},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"部族祭司","text":"现在听你这么说，我多多少少也理解了他不愿意回来的原因。","id":514},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"部族祭司","text":"这里从来没有人得过那样的疾病，他要是回来，面对他的病痛，我束手无策。要是再传染给其他人，估计我只会更加焦头烂额。","id":515},{"type":"character","name":"avg_344_beewax_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_070","focus":"1","id":516},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"所以......","id":517},{"type":"Dialog","id":518},{"type":"Character","id":519},{"type":"Text","text":"安克赫娜张开嘴，却发现接下来的话无论如何也说不出来了。","id":520},{"type":"Text","text":"一个人若决意要穿越一片大沙漠，便不能再回头，因为顺着风向流动的沙丘必然会吞没来时的路途。","id":521},{"type":"Text","text":"而那些为了走向未来而好不容易积蓄起的勇气，往往也并不足以让人回头直视面目全非的过去。","id":522},{"type":"Dialog","id":523},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":524},{"type":"Character","id":525},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":526},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_desert_3","screenadapt":"showall","id":527},{"type":"CameraEffect","effect":"Grayscale","amount":"0.8","keep":"true","id":528},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":529},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":530},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"忧愁的老人","text":"唉——","id":531},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"部落长老","text":"老家伙，当着孩子的面不要唉声叹气，会给她们带来霉运的。","id":532},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"忧愁的老人","text":"你这老东西，自己白胡子一大把还好意思说我老。你自己看看，今年游历回来的人只有往年的一半，这样下去怎么是好。","id":533},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"部落长老","text":"我又怎么能左右这些年轻人的想法，见识过部落之外的精彩纷呈，又有几个人愿意返回这里安于一隅呢？","id":534},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"忧愁的老人","text":"你这样坦然，部落迟早有一天要沦落到朝不保夕的境地。","id":535},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"部落长老","text":"我也是无计可施，总不能扣着那些孩子不许他们离开吧。","id":536},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"忧愁的老人","text":"（无奈摇头）","id":537},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"部落长老","text":"对了，还有一件事要同你商量，前些天我收到了一封信，里面提到一件事让我很不安。","id":538},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"忧愁的老人","text":"怎么了？","id":539},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"部落长老","text":"有个孩子得了那种病想要回来......","id":540},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"忧愁的老人","text":"好事哪，回来好啊。","id":541},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"部落长老","text":"他说自己身患绝症，怕回到部落会传染族人......可看孩子流落在外，我还是不忍心。","id":542},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"忧愁的老人","text":"这可如何是好？","id":543},{"type":"Dialog","id":544},{"type":"character","name":"avg_426_billro_1#6$1","name2":"avg_344_beewax_1#4$1","fadetime":"1","id":545},{"type":"Delay","time":"1.5","id":546},{"type":"character","name":"avg_426_billro_1#6$1","name2":"avg_344_beewax_1#4$1","focus":"1","id":547},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"卡涅利安","text":"......","id":548},{"type":"character","name":"avg_426_billro_1#6$1","name2":"avg_344_beewax_1#4$1","focus":"2","id":549},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_clothmovement","volume":"1","id":550},{"type":"move","name":"right","xpos":"5","fadetime":"0.2","block":"true","id":551},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"0.2","block":"true","id":552},{"type":"move","name":"right","xpos":"-5","fadetime":"0.2","block":"true","id":553},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"（扽扽卡涅利安的袖子）","id":554},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":555},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"姐姐......","id":556},{"type":"character","name":"avg_426_billro_1#1$1","name2":"avg_344_beewax_1#4$1","focus":"1","id":557},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"卡涅利安","text":"怎么了，安克赫娜？","id":558},{"type":"character","name":"avg_426_billro_1#1$1","name2":"avg_344_beewax_1#4$1","focus":"2","id":559},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"再过一年你就要去外面游历了，出去了，你还会回来吗？","id":560},{"type":"character","name":"avg_426_billro_1#6$1","name2":"avg_344_beewax_1#4$1","focus":"1","id":561},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"卡涅利安","text":"安克赫娜，我当然会回来，只是......","id":562},{"type":"character","name":"avg_426_billro_1#6$1","name2":"avg_344_beewax_1#4$1","focus":"2","id":563},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"姐姐？","id":564},{"type":"character","name":"avg_426_billro_1#6$1","name2":"avg_344_beewax_1#4$1","focus":"1","id":565},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"卡涅利安","text":"我只是不清楚祂对我究竟有怎样的安排，如果祂并不想我留下呢？","id":566},{"type":"character","name":"avg_426_billro_1#6$1","name2":"avg_344_beewax_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":567},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"不会的......姐姐离开后，我会一直向祂祈祷，只要是祂的儿女，所居之处必将远离邪秽。","id":568},{"type":"character","name":"avg_426_billro_1#6$1","name2":"avg_344_beewax_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":569},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"卡涅利安","text":"那不是邪秽，安克赫娜，不是的......","id":570},{"type":"Dialog","id":571},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":572},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":573},{"type":"character","id":574},{"type":"CameraEffect","effect":"Grayscale","fadetime":"0","amount":"0","block":"true","id":575},{"type":"Background","image":"31_g2_luo_reception","screenadapt":"showall","id":576},{"type":"Delay","time":"4","id":577},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":578},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$warm_intro","key":"$warm_loop","volume":"0.4","id":579,"musicid":3},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":580},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$doorknockquite","volume":"1","id":581},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":582},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_090","id":583},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"办事处干员","text":"哪位啊？","id":584},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_090","focus":"-1","id":585},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"卡蒂姆先生，是我，安克赫娜，麻烦你开开门好吗？","id":586},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_090","id":587},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"办事处干员","text":"来了来了。","id":588},{"type":"Dialog","id":589},{"type":"character","id":590},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$dooropenquite","volume":"1","id":591},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.51","id":592},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_090","name2":"avg_344_beewax_1#4$1","focus":"1","id":593},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"办事处干员","text":"安克赫娜小姐，你不是应该在游历途中吗？怎么样，东西送到了吗？","id":594},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_090","name2":"avg_344_beewax_1#4$1","focus":"2","id":595},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"呼——呼——","id":596},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_090","name2":"avg_344_beewax_1#4$1","focus":"1","id":597},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"办事处干员","text":"你还是先进来坐着缓口气吧。来，喝口水。","id":598},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_090","name2":"avg_344_beewax_1#4$1","focus":"2","id":599},{"type":"multiline","name":"安克赫娜","text":"我送到了......","id":600},{"type":"multiline","name":"安克赫娜","delay":"0.2","text":"咕咚咕咚，","id":601},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_090","name2":"avg_344_beewax_1#7$1","focus":"2","id":602},{"type":"multiline","name":"安克赫娜","text":"然后和当地的祭司一起好好安葬了他。","id":603},{"type":"Dialog","id":604},{"type":"Dialog","id":605},{"type":"Dialog","id":606},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_090","name2":"avg_344_beewax_1#7$1","focus":"1","id":607},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"办事处干员","text":"那就好，你回来不会就是为了向我汇报结果吧？","id":608},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"办事处干员","text":"看你这一头大汗，不是说了不必专门回来这一趟吗？","id":609},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_090","name2":"avg_344_beewax_1#7$1","focus":"2","id":610},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"不是的，我想到了，想到了自己要做什么。","id":611},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_090","name2":"avg_344_beewax_1#7$1","focus":"1","id":612},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"办事处干员","text":"哈哈哈，你的游历有目标了？快给我讲讲。","id":613},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_090","name2":"avg_344_beewax_1#3$1","focus":"2","id":614},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"我要去罗德岛，去它的本舰！","id":615},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安克赫娜","text":"那里有些东西，我想要带回到部落里面。","id":616},{"type":"Dialog","id":617},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"0.6","id":618},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"0.8","block":"true","id":619},{"type":"Text","text":"这句话她讲得是如此铿锵有力，全然不似往常柔软的语调，像窗外那颗沉甸甸的夕阳，狠狠砸在焦黄的大漠上。","id":620},{"type":"Text","text":"而她额间的标记，在这轮夕阳的照耀下，熠熠闪光。","id":621},{"type":"Dialog","id":622},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":623},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":624},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":625},{"type":"Character","id":626},{"type":"Image","id":627}],"characters":["安克赫娜","办事处干员","见多识广的老人","驮兽","博闻强识的妇人","沙漠行商","？？？","部族祭司","忧愁的老人","部落长老","卡涅利安"]}